mihon-ios is a native iOS (Swift/SwiftUI) port of Mihon. It includes and derives
from work in the Mihon source code — data models, wire/serialization formats,
algorithms, and runtime behavior reimplemented in Swift, using the Mihon source
as the reference specification.

